nodes.text: The following events took place in 232 BBY.

The Living Force Campaign Guide mentions that the rediscovery of the Cularin system took place 200 years before the Invasion of Naboo, which is dated to 32 BBY by The New Essential Chronology. It can therefore be deduced that the rediscovery took place in 232 BBY.
